<br><span style="font-weight: bold;">戒圍測量方法：</span>
<br>1.&nbsp;將軟尺或線繞著要測量的手指最寬處一圈，剛好貼合不要太緊。<br>2.&nbsp;在線的交會處做記號。軟皮尺讀取刻度。<br>3. 將線拉直，用尺測量長度，參照下方尺寸表，選擇適合自己的尺寸。<br>4. 重複以上步驟3-5次，確保測量出正確的戒圍。<br><br>*測量現已擁有且尺寸合適的戒指直徑和戒圍。<br><br>*因氣溫體溫可能會影響尺寸的測量結果，建議早晚分別測量，選擇最適合自己的尺寸。<br><br>* 我們的男士戒指，大多都是寬戒設計，因此在測量出您的戒圍後，推薦加大半個～一個尺寸。<br><br>*如您的關節比手指根部大，為確保戒指可以穿戴進去，或需要測量手指的關節尺寸。<br></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-144_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-145_"><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-146_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(53, 105, 166);"></span>尺寸選擇如有任何疑問，或希望客製特別尺寸，請隨時聯絡我們的<a href="/pages/contact-us" target="_self"><span style="color: rgb(53, 105, 166);">客服專員</span></a>。</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-148_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-149_"><div data-pf-type="Divider2" class="sc-dkmVhU NzRKb pf-150_ pf-divider-1"></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-154_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-155_"><div class="sc-epAKVu jszIJi pf-156_ pf-table-hover" data-pf-type="Table"><table class="pf-inner-table"><tbody><tr><th class="A1"><span>戒指內圍</span></th><th class="B1"><span>內直徑<br></span></th><th class="C1"><span>US</span></th><th class="D1"><span>UK</span></th><th class="E1"><span>EU</span></th><th class="F1"><span>HK</span></th></tr><tr><td class="A2"><span>48.5mm</span></td><td class="B2"><span>15.45mm</span></td><td class="C2"><span>#4½</span></td><td class="D2"><span>I½</span></td><td class="E2"><span>#48.5</span></td><td class="F2"><span>#10</span></td></tr><tr><td class="A3"><span>50.5mm</span></td><td class="B3"><span>16.08mm</span></